706723f-a.folder: Sheepshead Bay Road & 5th Street (West), Brooklyn, NY
706723f-a.text:
N.W. corner of Sheepshead Bay Rd. & W.5h St., Coney Island.
Sept. 23, 1941
P.L. Sperr, photographer

This photo seems to be placed at Bay Parkway not Sheepshead Bay Road.  Sheepshead Bay Road doesn't exist at West 5th Street anymore.  It disappeared when the seven 23 story buildings called Trump Village was constructed.

This picture should be place on West 5th Street between Neptune Avenues and West Brighton Avenue.
